## Components

### Data Sources
- Customers
- Products
- Orders
- Web Events

### ETL Layer
- Data Validation
- Duplicate Removal
- Null Handling
- Data Quality Checks

### Analytics Layer
- Revenue Analysis
- Customer Lifetime Value (CLV)
- Funnel Analysis
- Cohort Analysis
- Retention Analysis

### Reporting Layer
- Power BI Executive Dashboard
- Customer 360 Dashboard
- Product Performance Dashboard
- Funnel Dashboard
- Cohort Dashboard

### Business Outcome
Provides actionable insights into customer behavior, revenue trends, product performance, and customer retention.
